      "Title": "Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbContextAssertionException",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbContextAssertionException.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Thrown when a <xref href=\"Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbSetAssertions%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> assertion fails. Carries an\nEF-aware failure message that identifies the entity type and the specific check that\ndid not pass.</p>\n"
