      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbContextAssertionsExtensions",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbContextAssertionsExtensions.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Entry-point extensions that produce a <xref href=\"Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbSetAssertions%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> from a\n<xref href=\"Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.DbSet%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> or <xref href=\"System.Linq.IQueryable%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>. Intended to be\nimported via <code>using Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions;</code> in test files so\nthat <code>context.Set&lt;Product&gt;().Should()</code> resolves.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbSetAssertions-1.yml",
      "output": {
