      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbSetAssertions<TEntity>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbSetAssertions-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Fluent, chainable assertions over an <xref href=\"System.Linq.IQueryable%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> — either a\n<xref href=\"Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.DbSet%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> directly or a filtered query derived from one — for use\nin DbContextBuilder-backed tests. Each method runs the corresponding query\nasynchronously, throws <xref href=\"Wolfgang.DbContextBuilderCore.Assertions.DbContextAssertionException\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> with an EF-aware\nmessage on failure, and returns <code>this</code> so the next assertion can be chained.</p>\n"
    },
